John Young Program name: Word Puzzle App

Description: This app allows a user to enter in a sentence which will return the sentence with the vowels replaced with "-". The results will appear on a new page so that another person can try and guess the results.

Ruby Setup Gems used: Sinatra, Sinatra-contrib, rspec, capybara, and pry. Bundler must be installed.

Copying/license: The MIT License (MIT)

Play it live on: https://mysterious-shelf-3613.herokuapp.com/

